<p:sld xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships" xmlns:p="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main"><p:cSld><p:spTree><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="1" name=""/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="0" y="0"/><a:ext cx="0" cy="0"/><a:chOff x="0" y="0"/><a:chExt cx="0" cy="0"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="8195" name="Rectangle 3"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="body" idx="1"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="727242" y="322640"/><a:ext cx="9483558" cy="6082373"/></a:xfrm></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="2400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:effectLst><a:outerShdw blurRad="38100" dist="38100" dir="2700000" algn="tl"><a:srgbClr val="000000"><a:alpha val="43137"/></a:srgbClr></a:outerShdw></a:effectLst><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Rapportsynopsis som forarbejde til rapport – uddannelsesmæssig kontekst</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="600"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Synopsen som forarbejde til en (eksamens)rapport bruges ved videregående uddannelser – og er i denne forbindelse at betragte som et ”arbejdspapir”</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:spcBef><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcBef><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="1200"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1600" u="sng" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Synopsen kan og vil ændres undervejs</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>, hvis det viser sig, efter læsning af mere faglitteratur eller arbejdet med dit projekt, at hovedvægten skal lægges på noget andet, end det som du oprindelig skrev i din synopsis. Den endelige synopsis kan anvendes i din projektrapport i kondenseret form.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:spcBef><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcBef><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="2400"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t> En rapportsynopsis kan/skal altid så udførligt som I kan, 2-3 sider – indeholde disse punkter: </a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Problemstilling:</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t> emneområde, baggrund for overhovedet at stille problemformuleringens spørgsmål</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Problemformulering:</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t> det meget kontant formulerede spørgsmål, som din endelige konklusion skal være svaret på</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Overvejelser over </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>teori og metode</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>: din faglige indfaldsvinkel til emnet og den rent praktiske måde, du vil gennemføre undersøgelsen på</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Empiri:</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t> de data eller andre kilder, du vil bruge som grundlag for undersøgelsen</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Første udkast til </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>disposition</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>: helt uforpligtende på dette tidspunkt om end obligatorisk*</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Første udkast til </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>kildefortegnelse</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>: den litteratur om emnet du har kendskab til på forhånd, også helt uforpligtende.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="3657600" lvl="8" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1200" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>						(Salling, SDU, 2016)</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="da-DK" sz="1400" b="1" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Det er vigtigt, at din vejleder godkender din synopsis, inklusiv din problemformulering. Dette skal ske inden for tre uger efter semesterstart. </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="da-DK" sz="1600" u="sng" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:rPr><a:t>Deadline for at sende anmodning til din vejleder er den 16. februar 2026 kl. 10.00).</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="da-DK" sz="1600" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:endParaRPr lang="da-DK" altLang="da-DK" sz="1800" dirty="0"><a:latin typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:cs typeface="Calibri Light" panose="020F0302020204030204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="2160564940"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>